## Deskripsi : 
To solve this challenge, you'll need to analyze the provided PCAP file and track down the attack method. The attacker has cleverly concealed his moves in well timely manner. Dive into the network traffic, apply the right filters and show off your forensic prowess and unmask the digital intruder!

<br>

## Petunjuk :

1.Filter your packets to narrow down your search.
2.Attacks were done in timely manner.
3.Time is essential

<br>

## Pengerjaan
Kita diberikan file PCAP,File PCAP (Packet Capture) adalah format penyimpanan data lalu lintas jaringan komputer yang merekam paket data mentah.

Disini kita menggunakan tool wireshark

Pada tool wireshark masukkan file PCAP tadi

Sesuai petunjuk urutkan waktunya

Klik baris paling atas lalu klik Retransmitted TCP Segment data,lalu show packet bytes dan decode ke base 64

Flag disusun secara terbalik dari atas
